()Authoritative source (HR system) kya hai?
--1️⃣ Authoritative Source kya hota hai?
Ye wo system hai jahan se SailPoint identity attributes (user info, roles, department, email, etc.) ko verify karta hai.
Mostly HR system ko authoritative source maana jata hai, kyunki HR me employee ka official record hota hai.
SailPoint me aggregation process ke through ye data fetch hota hai

Example: HR System as Authoritative Source
HR system me Rahul ka record:-
EmployeeID: EMP12345
Name: Rahul Kumar
Email: rahul@company.com
Department: Finance
Role: Finance Manager
Cost Center: CC1001
Status: Active

💡 Tip bhai:-
Sirf HR system nahi, aur bhi systems ho sakte hain jaise:
Active Directory → AD accounts
Finance system → Cost Center data
ERP system → Project assignments

--SailPoint aggregation:-
Identity rahul = aggregateFromHR("EMP12345"); 
// Ab Rahul ki identity SailPoint me ready hai
Authoritative source ka fayda:-
SailPoint me official data hamesha HR se sync hota hai
Manual updates ki zarurat kam hoti hai
Policies aur workflows automatically apply ho sakte hain.